         </xocs:funding>
         <xocs:funding-text>This research was undertaken in collaboration between Forest Research Institute (IBL), Poland, and IDEAS NCBR, Poland. We would like to express our gratitude to IDEAS NCBR for their invaluable contribution to this research project, made possible through a scholarship granted to Y.E. Remote sensing data acquisition and field data collection from Bia\u0142owie\u017Ca Forest were conducted as part of the project \u201CAssessment and monitoring of biodiversity of the Bia\u0142owie\u017Ca Forest based on selected natural elements \u2013 continuation\u201D, funded by the General Directorate of the State Forests in Warsaw (contract number MZ.271.3.7.2022 , internal no. 500483 ). </xocs:funding-text>
